             was indicted for <rs id="t17930529-42-off226" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17930529-42-off226" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17930529-42-off226" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17930529-42-cd227" type="crimeDate">15th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930529-42-off226 t17930529-42-cd227"></join>, in the dwelling house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17930529-42-victim545" type="victimName">
