                  , a promissary note called a bank note, value 20 l. No. 4,822, the said note being the property of the said 
                     <persName id="t17930529-42-person550">
                        Bridget
                         Maclaurin
                     <interp inst="t17930529-42-person550" type="surname" value="Maclaurin"></interp>
